          Fresh, fast, and delicious food delivered right to your door. Experience the taste that keeps you coming back.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 animate-fade-in">
          <a 
            href="/menu" 
            class="bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all transform hover:scale-105 text-center"
          >
            View Menu
          </a>
          <a 
            href="/order" 
            class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-red-600 transition-all text-center"
          >
            Order Now
